C. V., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0330 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 29, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because C.V. has failed to serve an initial brief as provided by this court's order of April 10, 2018, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

NORTHCUTT, BADALAMENTI, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
